===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}

A word generally associated with the [[Eurovision Song Contest]], although the word 'Eurovision' actually refers to the signal used to transmit events broadcast by the [[European Broadcasting Union]]. Other events with the name 'Eurovision' are also the [[Junior Eurovision Song Contest]] and the [[Eurovision Dance Contest]].

